➜西安最解馋猪脚饭，香到流口水，饭菜还能无限加！
http://www.sohu.com/a/420971677_348928	10425
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/9fb16a7f1eaa42c6a9023730b37f8bd1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各具风格的装修，精致的餐品&amp;摆盘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这个人人都追求要精致生活的时代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各种高端餐厅、网红店</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纷纷刷屏了我们的社交圈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但在这其中，总有几家路边小馆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有多么精致的装修和摆盘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仅凭借着口味和热情的服务</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就俘获了一众西安吃货的心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/d54e0ee4368b4d26bb6dcb2433e5a384.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最近就有一家名为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">【陆长久古法猪脚饭】的店</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">凭借独树一帜的店铺风格</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和正宗的古法隆江猪脚饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">频频刷屏西安人的社交圈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/163bd820e30c43669ef57b4c4f9f745b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>虽然说重庆没有重庆鸡公煲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但是，隆江猪脚饭它真的就是在隆江</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在广东，无论是CBD的白领</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是手下几栋楼的包租公</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又或是街头穿着夹板的靓仔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都会有那一碗钟情的隆江猪脚饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/f92c5134efa74ab9861fa0d32aa70200.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">走进这条巷子，你很难不注意到他家店</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为门口的招牌实在是太太太显眼了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红色的横幅上印着两行大大的字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“疫情原因，无力装修</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要吃正宗，要吃味道，请进”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如此“任性”的店不仅想让人去一探究竟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200926/d17b60df4d214cc6ad406cf27b13c61b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从小小的门口进入后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">店内一定会让你再次发出感叹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/0ad324f89ccd425dac2950b11df74e97.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">墙面上全是用旧报纸贴上的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这个浮华的时代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如此朴实无华的小店着实少见了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200926/0f4c36c552ee4e74a0be5d1c7732b117.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">店里面麻雀虽小，五脏俱全</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">容纳着三个桌子，可以在此用餐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板在操作台现做着猪脚饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200926/ba7259251bc043fbac5e963de3e94ee6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>听老板介绍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他家的肉都是每天现卤的，售完即止</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以经常会有很多人来晚可能就没有了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现卤的肉皮会呈现酱红色，肉是白色的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃起来口感也会更加鲜嫩，脂香浓郁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200926/d2353f070bde4f35895e34fb7a49cc6d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他家的配菜也是每天现做的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200926/2bc9adf8f8d84e648f74268c2fc6e78c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早听闻去晚了可能吃不到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以赶在他家开门时就到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新鲜的配菜也都还热乎着冒气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200926/7b3c398e88e343c8af4e8be5077f470d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">点好了一份古法猪脚饭后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板就开始做，出餐很快，几分钟就搞定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坐了一会发现他家的老顾客非常的多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每个进来的客人都和老板有说有笑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200926/c2a7772196c74784937fec45f91c4c20.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板也是个十分亲切幽默的大哥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贴心的询问着每个顾客的口味需求</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200926/5e81e477115e4309ba8a90c84b447b57.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不一会儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份热气腾腾的猪脚饭就上桌了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/8c056e88b3634c749c19a859983c9459.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给的猪脚分量超足，满满的铺在饭上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加上配菜，再浇一勺浓郁的卤汁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一大碗看起来都让人口水四溢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200926/28dd34e44eb14bc99d5d8e0570ae4a5e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份价格也不贵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">基本上都在十几块</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">饭菜还可以无限加</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">性价比可以说是很高了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200926/a4dea0b418cf4670b266151bada8bf80.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">卤好的猪脚，色香味俱全</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪皮入口弹嫩糯香，香气四溢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满满的胶原蛋白</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200926/98cd7ff574ab4826b3597218770cc2b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪肉入味十足，肥而不腻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再搭配上开胃的圆白菜和酸菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200926/3fe4f2709e9048b48467b98e99ac5e48.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一口肉、一口配菜、一口米饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃起来超爽！丝毫不会觉得腻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/a796f98dfb2f4a0aaf8acaeb573431cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200926/4e058f28a24f44a9b0120d9362d68ae8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另加的这份脆皮五花肉也十分好吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一上桌，香味就开始四处弥漫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200926/1ad1dc0cc45a4cf0bf9a910740440fe1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五花肉经过油炸后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">外皮焦脆，肉香浓郁，口感极好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200926/fd4735ee3c3f48819c69998ba41599d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有很多可以另加的小吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">卤鹌鹑蛋、潮汕肉卷都非常不错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200926/77f16e2891d94439b103802936c33ccc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200926/f128cee5c13148ff97afbc50adc1ef2a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但建议大家适量加菜哦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为分量真的挺多，当心吃不完浪费</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/387e14fb27a7409698d01e748399e797.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样一碗十几块的猪脚饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅能吃到肉还能吃饱吃好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难怪成了西安无数吃货的心头爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>地址请在扑通后台回复“猪脚饭”查看</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200926/b4a2cef64e66430e812f52eed8e47066.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>